description: Terrorism Close Calls: Series 1 Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Dylan Berry and Edinho Moreno, published by Netflix in 2018 - English narration http://docuwiki.net/images/e/e5/Terrorism-Close-Calls-Series-1-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ Terrorism Close Calls: Series 1 7) Plot to Kill U.S. Soldiers - 2007 Although they plan to strike in Germany, their targets are American soldiers who frequent popular nightclubs and bars as well as at the Ramstein Airbase. The plot to kill "many" US soldiers is considered one of the most significant homegrown terrorists threats to Germany and would launch a nine-month undercover surveillance operation. Once arrested all four suspects issued lengthy confessions calling their intended plot a "defensive jihad" and retaliation of what they saw as America's war against Islam.
